criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Elective Surgeries;

          -  Aged 60 years and over;

          -  Being fasting;

          -  Verbalize thirst;

          -  Have been approved in the assesment of Safety Protocol of Thirst Management (SPTM)

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with ingestion and swallowing restrictions;

          -  Patients with self-reported allergy to mint;
